GSD.product_version: versions from v5.6 to before v6.0.9
GSD.description:
octeontx2-pf: Fix SQE threshold checking

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v6.0.9 by commit 015e3c0a3b16193aab23beefe4719484b9984c2d, it was introduced in version v5.6 by commit 3ca6c4c882a7f34085b170d93cf0d0e843aa00e6. For more details please see the references link.
